@startuml
title ABC Company Payroll System - Actors & Roles

actor "HR Admin
(User: HR0001)" as HR
actor "Employee" as EMP
actor "Payroll Dept
(Printer/File Consumer)" as PAY
actor "HR Sign-Off" as SIGN

rectangle "Django Payroll Web App" as APP {
  usecase "Login" as UC_LOGIN
  usecase "Manage Employees
(Add/Edit/Delete/Search)" as UC_EMP
  usecase "Manage Salary & Benefits" as UC_SAL
  usecase "Enter Hours & PTO" as UC_TIME
  usecase "Submit Time Entry" as UC_SUBMIT
  usecase "Calculate Payroll
(Lock Time Entries)" as UC_CALC
  usecase "View Paycheck Breakdown" as UC_VIEW
  usecase "Generate Reports
(HR Review)" as UC_REPORT
  usecase "Export Payroll File
(CSV for printing)" as UC_EXPORT
  usecase "View Application Info
(Version)" as UC_INFO
}

HR --> UC_LOGIN
HR --> UC_EMP
HR --> UC_SAL
HR --> UC_CALC
HR --> UC_REPORT
HR --> UC_EXPORT
HR --> UC_INFO

EMP --> UC_LOGIN
EMP --> UC_TIME
EMP --> UC_SUBMIT
EMP --> UC_VIEW

SIGN --> UC_REPORT
SIGN --> UC_EXPORT

PAY --> UC_EXPORT

note right of UC_CALC
Pretax deductions (medical)
are applied before taxes.
end note

note bottom of UC_TIME
Hourly rules:
- >8/day = 1.5x
- Saturday = 1.5x
Salary rules:
- Paid 8h Mon-Fri
- PTO only entry
end note

@enduml
